item.title: Warning signs on Mexican beach declare area restricted by U.S.
item.description: The signs read in English and Spanish, "Warning: Restricted Area" and had been declared restricted by "the commander."

item.title: Owl partly covered in concrete after getting into cement mixer rescued in Utah
item.description: An owl found partially encased in concrete after it got inside a cement mixer in Utah is expected to fly free again after it was painstakingly cleaned...

item.title: Person in custody after woman set on fire on CTA Blue Line train
item.description: A person was in custody Tuesday after a woman was set on fire while riding a CTA Blue Line in Chicago's Loop the night before.

item.title: Poland accuses Russia of "state terror" with railway sabotage attack
item.description: Polish Prime Minister Donald Tusk said two Ukrainian citizens working for Russia are suspected of blowing up a railway line in Poland over the weekend...

item.title: Comey to challenge his indictment for "vindictive and selective" prosecution
item.description: In court Wednesday, former FBI Director James Comey will try to have the criminal charges against him dismissed.
